  "couplingIntensity": "None",
  "created": "2026-03-16",
  "description": "The mod wheel performs the fundamental granular transformation in real time: wheel at 0 = grain size 0.7 — large fragments, recognizable sound shapes moving slowly through the source buffer. Wheel at 127 = grain size 0.05 — texture and fog, all identifiable shape dissolved. The performance is the journey between. Aftertouch adds posScatter — pressing hard breaks the orderly playhead and randomizes each grain's starting position. Start with a held chord, wheel up slowly. Watch recognition dissolve.",
